  1. Since the data seems lack of categorical variables, we will create a few categorical variables for easier visualization. From the Date variable create three categorical variables to record weekdays, months and quarters. You could also create a categorical variable to record the state regions (South, North East, Midwest, West) or other new categorical variables.
library(lubridate)
df$Date <- ymd(df$Date)

df$month = month(df$Date)

df$weekday = wday(df$Date)

df$quarter = quarters(df$Date)
